rpgonline.abt

Class ABTDataInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • java.io.FilterInputStream
        • java.io.DataInputStream
          • rpgonline.abt.ABTDataInputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, DataInput, AutoCloseable

    public class ABTDataInputStream
extends DataInputStream
    An extension of DataInputStream to provide functions and formats needed by ABT. This format is compatible with ABTDataOutputStream
    Author:
    Tomas
    See Also:
    ABTDataOutputStream
